pageProduct.description:

General Information

Eye mask infused with a brightening eye serum which reduces the appearance of dark circles for bright, youthful looking eyes.

  • Instantly illuminate and refresh tired-looking eyes
  • Reduces the visible appearance of dark circles and puffiness
  • Nourishes and calms the eye area

Powerful triple action eye serum targets the entire eye area for bright, youthful looking eyes. Vitamins C and B3, Coffee Bean and Green Tea brighten dark circles and restore radiance to tired looking eyes.

Ingredients

Water, Butylene Glycol, Glycereth-26, Propylene Glycol, Niacinamide, Bis-PEG-18 Methyl Ether Dimethyl Silane, Rosa Centifolia Flower Water, Betaine, PEG-60 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Allantoin, Chondrus Crispus (Carrageenan), Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract, Coffea Arabica (Coffee) Seed Extract, Diospyros Kaki Leaf Extract, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Extract, Wine Extract, Dipotassium Glycyrrhizate, Tocopheryl Acetate, Polyglutamic Acid , Morus Alba Bark Extract, Ascorbyl Glucoside, Ascorbic Acid, Disodium EDTA, Carbomer, Triethanolamine, Methylparaben, Propylparaben, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Parfum/Fragrance.

Directions

Cleanse skin. Place the eye mask over the eye area, close eye flaps over the eyelids if desired. Wear for 30 minutes. Remove eye mask, do not rinse. Excess serum can be applied to the face and neck.
